title: Previewing Deciding Week 5 Games in Big Ten West & Big 12
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and Stanford Steve are joined by Minnesota head coach PJ Fleck to talk about the undefeated Golden Gophers and the Big Ten West. In addition, Jay Walker and Tiffany Greene go across the world of HBCU football and break down the wild, wild west of SWAC West football. Plus, the crew discusses which Big 12 teams have to get a win this season and what undefeated Kansas has to do to garner national respect.
